Maximiliano Hernández https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maximiliano_Hern%C3%A1ndez 0 Maximiliano Hernández (born September 12, 1973) is an American actor. He is best known for portraying Agent Jasper Sitwell in the Marvel Cinematic Universe and FBI Agent Chris Amador in the first season of The Americans.
